        Parameters:
        parameters - of the search
        hashingStrategy - strategy to factor results
        mapper - function that maps results to their mapping counterparts.
        Returns:
        query to perform the search. Obtained results are mapped to whatever objects that are automatically filtered wrt. equals() relation. Storing mapped objects instead of original elements may be wise wrt to memory consumption.
